name: Towering Splash GX Box
extCardText: The Pokemon TCG: Towering Splash GX Box brings two Water Type Pokemon together, the Magikarp and the Wailord to make a mighty splash. The Tag Team Pokemon will appear together on a foil promo card and an oversize foil card. Together Magikarp and Wailord GX boast 300 HP – the biggest HP total in the Pokemon TCG. The box also includes four Pokemon TCG boosters and a code card for the online game.
